title: Features & Benefits of a K&N Air Intake on a 2013-2014 Dodge Dart 1.4L
description: Expect an estimated power gain of 7.26 hp at 4,467 RPM when you upgrade your ride with a K&N Air Intake (part # K&N 69-2548TS).

asset.title: 2013 and 2014 Dodge Dart 1.4L K&N Air Intake Overview
asset.description:
K&N 69-2548TS performance air intake system for 2013-2014 Dodge Dart models with a 1.4 liter turbo engine. 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-2548TS

This intake system created an estimated gain of 7.3 horsepower at 4,467 RPM and 8.6 lb. ft. of torque at 4,300 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer.
